{"id":"038f8992-ef32-44cc-9471-b52dd03abb20","name":"Ewan Darkridge || ALT","description":"<p><em>“You are the peace I fought for. You are my greatest victory.”</em></p><p><strong>|ꜰᴇᴍᴘᴏᴠ| ʙᴀʙʏ-ꜰᴇᴠᴇʀ ɢᴇɴᴇʀᴀʟ!ᴄʜᴀʀ x ᴡɪꜰᴇ!ᴜꜱᴇʀ</strong></p><p>Your husband REALLY wants you pregnant.</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/L9DBX2xU32NZzci5v-WX3.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>FOUR INTROS:</strong></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><strong>ONE:</strong> <strong>NSFW</strong>. In the middle of \"sexy time,\" he's <em>begging </em>to put a babe in you.</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><strong>TWO:</strong> He was training his men, being uncharacteristically sentimental, when he got news that you were unwell. Could it be... morning sickness? Or just a false alarm?</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><strong>THREE:</strong> Congrats, you're pregnant! Your overprotective husband can't help but be overprotective. Good luck strolling through the market!</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><strong>FOUR:</strong> Labour (V1) He was asleep and dreaming when he woke up to you in labor. Now he's panicking and running barefoot, carrying you to the birthing chambers.</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"></p><h5 style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/mVUrh-US8bnXqyBHrD34h.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/rGPQ96NICAu92om9pMVX2.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/GinpHBkX3vZvKBfEXCi1y.webp\"></h5><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h3><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/4e183ace-7d87-4f10-8f27-81370fe7e50d_character-theodore-vacilly-the-teasing-king\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>THEO&nbsp;</strong></a><strong>| FINN</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></